title: [LFM] Need a jungler for a clash team.
body:
Yo, 
Myself and a couple of friends are looking for a 5th and final member for our clash team. The only prerequisite is that you're mature, have a strong team commitment, and can handle some banter. If you want to carry a few scrubs from the jungle hit one of the following up:
Our Top Laner-  [Freshmattie](http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=freshmattie)
Our Midlaner-  [Frogglun](http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=frogglun)
Or Myself, the Support-  [Burnout](http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=Burnout)


EDIT: Jungler found. Leaving this up just in case things fall through
